sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Production Supervisor
    participant FE as Frontend (ProductionEntry.jsx)
    participant API as API (productionRoutes.js)
    participant DB as MongoDB (Machine/Production)

    User->>FE: Select Machine & Date
    User->>FE: Enter Meter Reading (Current)
    FE->>FE: Calculate Production (Current - Previous)
    User->>FE: Click "Update"
    FE->>API: POST /api/production/update
    API->>DB: Find Machine
    API->>DB: Save DailyProduction Record
    API->>DB: Update Machine (totalProduction, avgEfficiency)
    DB-->>API: Success
    API-->>FE: 200 OK (Updated Data)
    FE->>User: Show Success Message
    FE->>FE: Update Efficiency Bar & Status
